We're kicking off our first est film production with a momentous Malvern Home renovation by @dohertydesignstudio from est magazine issue #35.
.
Tapping into its rich architectural past and 1980s new wave bones, @dohertydesignstudio have skilfully commandeered an epic journey to reinvent this Melbourne family home. An original 1980's design by architect Peter McIntyre. .
.
Experience the entire home via the link in profile or read the full feature in est magazine issue #35. .
.

.
View all three films via link in profile.
.

Creative Direction | Design @robmillsarchitects

HOME TOUR | Casa Azul
.
The municipality of Grândola, located in Alentejo, is renowned for its red wine, vast olive groves and cork forests.
​.
​It’s here where a group of four friends decided to purchase four plots of land together, engaging Lisbon-based architecture firm @bakgordonarquitectos to sensitively construct a holiday home that appears as an extension of the arid landscape.
​.
​See more of this family holiday home on estliving.com – link in profile. 
​.
​Design @bakgordonarquitectos
​Photography @francisconogueira
​.
​https://www.estliving.com/casa-azul-bak-gordon/

HOME TOUR | Harvey House 
​.
​@marmolradziner took on the weighted brief of restoring the Harvey House, originally designed by ​Buff & Hensman in 1969, located in Palm Springs, California.
​.
Originally designed to blur the boundaries between indoors and outdoors,  ​@marmolradziner introduced terrazzo as the primary material throughout the Harvey House, to accentuate the relationship between the home, pool and pool house, together with the expansive, floor-to-ceiling glazing. 
​.
​Design @marmolradziner
​Photography Roger Davies & Giorgio Possenti
​.
​https://www.estliving.com/
